Name: Apply Payments
Description__c: Selects all customer invoices which are changed and pulls the list of Payment Details to sum up

Name: AccountingEntry Void Batch
Description__c: Regenerates the reversal accounting entries for source docs which are voided and Accrual journal entries

Name: MRP Planning
Description__c: Perform all material planning steps, including all outstanding SO demand, PO supply and item inventory, work in process and generate a consolidated plan for this company

Name: MRP Item Leveling
Description__c: Ensure that each item in the item database has the correct item level information, this step is required prior to MRP demand generation whenever new items are added or item components or item assemblies are modified.

Name: Customer Invoicing With Grouping Rules
Description__c: Generates customer invoices based on grouping rules for the given company.

Name: Customer Invoice Accounting
Description__c: Generates accounting entries for all customer invoices, that are finalized but not yet accounted for, for the given company

Name: Payment Accounting
Description__c: Generates accounting entries for all Payments, that are finalized but not yet accounted, for the given company.

Name: Invoice Accounting
Description__c: Generates accounting entries for all Invoices, that are finalized but not yet accounted, for the given company.

Name: Customer Receipt Accounting
Description__c: Generates accounting entries for all customer receipts, which are finalized but not yet accounted for, for the given company.

Name: DTP Batch
Description__c: Days to Pay Batch job which updates DTPForecast date on all open customer Invoices used for Cashforecasting reports

Name: PO Receipt Accounting
Description__c: Generates accounting entries for all purchase order receipts, that have corresponding closed purchase orders, but not yet accounted for the given company.

Name: Supplier Invoice Accounting
Description__c: Generates accounting entries for all supplier invoices, that are finalized but not yet accounted for, for the given company.

Name: Supplier Payment Accounting
Description__c: Generates accounting entries for all payments made against supplier invoices, but not yet accounted for, for the given company.

Name: Journal Entry Accounting
Description__c: Generates accounting entries for all journal entries created, but not yet accounted for, for the given company.

Name: Fixed Asset Depreciation
Description__c: Runs through all the fixed assets that have been marked as depreciated and calculates their values based on the pre-defined algorithm for that asset class.

Name: Fixed Asset Depreciation Accounting
Description__c: Generates accounting entries for all the fixed assets that have been depreciated but not yet accounted for.

Name: Fixed Asset Adjustment Accounting
Description__c: Generates accounting entries for all the fixed assets that have been adjusted but not yet accounted for.

Name: Inventory Change Accounting
Description__c: Generates accounting entries for all inventory changes, which are finalized but not yet accounted for, for the given company.
